General.Name: I&I Group Public Company Limited
General.Description: I&I Group Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a digital and technology consulting company in Thailand. The company is involved in the design and installation of customer relationship management systems; rental of software systems; design, installation of enterprise resource planning systems; and distribution of software systems. It also engages in consulting business on brand strategy planning, customer experience management and digital marketing; and provision of personnel recruitment services in the information sector. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Ratchathewi, Thailand.
